{"tid":1201413,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普預期與華將達成協議 ","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:50:07.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53d282eb88cdf9b2b0271f6599081c8f2f9bfcaf","tid":1201413,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"中美就貿易戰談判仍處僵局，全球關注兩國領導人會否在月底於日本大阪舉行的G20峯會見面。美國總統特朗普在白宮向記者表示，自己與習近平預定在峯會上會談及會面，認為會發生有趣的事，拭目以待。他早前接受傳媒訪問時，預中美將達成協議，原因是中國不得不這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普較早前接受CNBC訪問，除提出若習近平不與他見面將加徵的關稅，及認為可將華為納入中美貿易協議內，他又批評中國將人民幣貶值，令中國有巨大競爭優勢，又指習近平實質上是中國「聯儲局」，即人民銀行的負責人，有能力直接影響貨幣政策，可以做他想做的事，例如貶值人民幣，放寬貨幣政策，或投放大量資金，抵銷美國加徵關稅的影響。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又指，自己與習近平的關系「很好」，他形容習近平「其實是個很棒的人」，是「了不起的人」，「很強有力、很聰明，但是他是為了中國，而我是為了美國。」<br />\n特朗普認為中國將與美國達成協議，「因為他們將不得不這樣做。」他指出：「目前中國絕對正在遭受重創，公司正在離開中國，去別的國家，包括我們國家，這是因為他們不想交關稅。根據很多事實、很多了解，我認為中國會達成協議的，因為他們必須要達成協議。」"},{"pid":"8931c5174f9ebcb934f42d1172ec87f0b647f0ac","tid":1201413,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"留名睇反口"},{"pid":"803a318abc7fdc04190182c8ac5029dbc13d63b6","tid":1201413,"uid":198008,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"g20 trump: winnie the xi is my dog"},{"pid":"7dc40098b2d5020914a09dbe06b335e687a2415d","tid":1201413,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"100% 撚狗戰術<br />\n佢一定拖到大選前先出大絕 ..."},{"pid":"e261e9a8f0f9e4eac2a2f54bb1ad2d3ce6c6401f","tid":1201413,"uid":85461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/71UgBNx7WmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F71UgBNx7WmL.jpg&h=5d61eacd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eed19d3a274796c26f99cd49013cd1d22fe11ce2","tid":1201413,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"成日出口術撚鳩班支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed2ea917daa62a0cbce93aaea0d0ff9f63d1a2c","tid":1201413,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"睇佢咁急就知無料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85f2799b684331466b4a5a3c17193cafc4fb7bf","tid":1201413,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"通常叫習近平做fd之後會害習習一獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3770f4f381863f97c4272a425ae0c2926a60228","tid":1201413,"uid":207894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86306bd0b5bc4d49eb01774fa38c849adf7ba71","tid":1201413,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:50:07.000Z","msg":"股市係一浪一浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}